pairs.key: Our domain's ground will carve a path.
pairs.value: 我们的领域将开辟出一条道路。

pairs.key: Tread upon our domain with care and it will respond in kind.
pairs.value: 小心踏入我们的领域，它会做出相应的回应。

pairs.key: May your desire blossom into a wildfire.
pairs.value: 愿你的愿望化作燎原之火。
万物顺从于我们的意志。

pairs.key: The soil whispers secrets of those who've walked before.
pairs.value: 泥土低语着前人的秘密。

pairs.key: Beneath the surface, our whispers guide fate.
pairs.value: 在表层之下，我们的低语指引着命运。

pairs.key: Our heartbeats sync with the world's tremors.
pairs.value: 我们的心跳与世界的震颤同步。

pairs.key: Our reach extends beyond the visible horizon.
pairs.value: 我们的触及范围延伸到地平线之外。

pairs.key: Careful planning and strategy may lead you.
pairs.value: 周密的计划和战略可让你受益匪浅。

pairs.key: A set choice; followed through and flawlessly executed.
pairs.value: 做出决定，贯彻到底，完美执行。

pairs.key: Chance's hand may favour your goals.
pairs.value: 机遇之手可将你推向目标。

pairs.key: In the dance of fate and strategy, precision reigns.
pairs.value: 在命运与战略的共舞中，精确是最重要的。

pairs.key: To foresee is to command the threads of destiny.
pairs.value: 远见就是掌握命运的脉搏。

pairs.key: Tread lightly on the line between choice and predestination.
pairs.value: 在选择和宿命之间，你要小心谨慎。

pairs.key: To conquer fate, first understand its riddles.
pairs.value: 要征服命运，首先要理解命运之谜。

pairs.key: A single instant, stretched to infinity.
Your future glows golden with possibility.
pairs.value: 你的未来充满无限可能，熠熠生辉。

pairs.key: Hasten and value every passing moment.
pairs.value: 抓紧时间，珍惜每分每秒。

pairs.key: With every heartbeat, an epoch is born.
pairs.value: 每一次心跳，都是一个时代的诞生。

pairs.key: The sands of time are fleeting; grasp them.
pairs.value: 时间之沙稍纵即逝，请把握住。

pairs.key: The dance of time is swift; miss not its rhythm.
pairs.value: 时间的舞步很快，不要错过它的节奏。

pairs.key: The pendulum of time swings but once for each moment.
pairs.value: 时间的钟摆每时每刻只摆动一次。
确保你的道路畅通无阻。

pairs.key: Our vigor may aid your conquest.
pairs.value: 我们的力量可助你征服。

pairs.key: Cherish this mote of my might.
Rise, like the waves, unyielding and fierce.
pairs.value: 崛起，如波涛汹涌，不屈不挠，勇往直前。

pairs.key: Forge ahead with the fury of storms.
pairs.value: 在暴风雨的狂暴中奋勇前进。

pairs.key: With relentless force, mold your path.
pairs.value: 用无情的力量塑造你的道路。

pairs.key: Harness my wrath to awaken the dormant.
pairs.value: 利用我的愤怒，唤醒沉睡的灵魂。

pairs.key: The harmony of the natural world eludes you.
pairs.value: 自然世界的和谐你难以理解。

pairs.key: The beauty of nature thrives on resilience, but your actions have brought only discord.
pairs.value: 自然之美源于顽强的生命力，但你的行为却只带来不和之音。

pairs.key: Your failures wither the very essence of life.
pairs.value: 你的失败让生命的本质凋零。

pairs.key: The song of nature laments your inadequacy.
pairs.value: 自然的歌声哀叹着你的不足。

pairs.key: You tarnish the purity of nature with your missteps.
pairs.value: 你的失误玷污了自然的纯洁。

pairs.key: Even the wisest can stumble on their path to enlightenment.
pairs.value: 即使是最聪明的人，也会在悟道的道路上磕磕绊绊。

pairs.key: Seek knowledge, learn from your failures, and you shall find your way.
pairs.value: 寻求知识，从失败中吸取教训，你就会找到自己的方向。

pairs.key: Failure is but a stepping stone on the road to enlightenment.
pairs.value: 失败只是通往启迪之路的一块垫脚石。

pairs.key: Even the most brilliant minds face setbacks.
pairs.value: 再聪明的人也会遇到挫折。

pairs.key: In the pursuit of wisdom, missteps are bound to occur.
pairs.value: 在追求智慧的过程中，难免会出现失误。

pairs.key: A moment lost is a chance wasted.
The sands of time never cease their relentless march.
pairs.value: 时间的流沙从未停止过无情的脚步。

pairs.key: In the grand tapestry of existence, your actions are but threads.
pairs.value: 在存在的宏大织锦中，你的行为只是小小线头。

pairs.key: Time's embrace can be both cruel and kind.
pairs.value: 时间的怀抱既残酷又仁慈。

pairs.key: As the clock ticks, so do your choices shape your destiny.
pairs.value: 随时间流逝，你的选择也将决定你的命运。

pairs.key: Perhaps you should consider a different path.
pairs.value: 也许你应该考虑换一条路。

pairs.key: Weakness is a burden that few can afford.
pairs.value: 软弱是一种负担，很少有人能承受得起。

pairs.key: Your feeble attempt have left much to be desired.
pairs.value: 你微弱的尝试还有很多不足。

pairs.key: A hunter must be swift to adapt, or they are doomed to fail.
pairs.value: 猎人必须迅速适应，否则注定失败。

pairs.key: No smiles will be cast upon those who crumble in the face of adversity.
pairs.value: 逆境中溃败之人不会得到微笑。
